'From Squeak2.6 of 11 October 1999 [latest update: #1754] on 4 January 2000 at 9:12:35 pm'!"Change Set:		AdvanceVersionDate:			4 January 2000Author:			Ted KaehlerThis update offers the choice to advance the Squeak verson number for the purpose of continuing to retrieve updates for Release 2.7 and beyond."!"Postscript:Offer the chance to Advance the version number."(self confirm: 'This is the last update for Squeak 2.6 and 2.7alpha.Do you wish to have your system marked as version 2.7so that you may retrieve updates for version 2.7 and beyond?')	ifTrue: [EToySystem eToyVersion: 'Squeak2.7' date: Date today.			PopUpMenu notify: 'You may now request updates againto retrieve updates for 2.7 and beyond.']	ifFalse: [PopUpMenu notify: 'The version will not change.'].!